imdb.plot outline: Chase Von Austin an over-privlaged actor from the mid-west and Chewy Guadalupe a once homeless screenwriter. Once Chewy inherits a sum of money from his deceased aunt he decides to chase his one true dream in life and become a screenplay writer. At the same time, Chase Von austin decides to leave his wholesome home town and take the plunge and move to Hollywood...
imdb.title: Ambitions in LALA Land
